Config Raspberry pi: 

NOOBS -> Raspbian

ip static : 
iface lo inet loopback
iface eth0 inet static
address 192.168.0.x // 48 -> gros 49, petit
netmask 255.255.255.0
network 192.168.0.254
broadcast 192.168.0.255
gateway 192.168.0.254

auto wlan0
allow-hotplug wlan0


